Sanell Aggenbach (amụrụ n'afọ 1975) bụ onye na-ese ihe na South Africa nke bi ma na-arụ ọrụ na Woodstock, Cape Town N'iji ihe osise, obibi akwụkwọ, na ihe ọkpụkpụ, ọrụ ya na-ekwu maka mmekọrịta dị n'etiti akụkọ ihe mere eme na akụkọ onwe ya, na mmetụta nke mgbagwoju anya. Ọrụ ya na-enyocha usoro nke nostalgia na akụkọ ifo akụkọ ihe mere eme, na-ejikarị ihe na-atọ ọchị, nke na-emebi ihe, na nke na-enweghị isi iji dọta onye na-ekiri ya na mkparịta ụka banyere isiokwu ndị gbara ọchịchịrị.  O nwere ụdị pụrụ iche nke ijikọta usoro eserese ọdịnala na ihe ọkpụkpụ, yana ọrụ aka ụmụ nwanyị dịka ịkwa akwa na tapestry.

Aggenbach gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Stellenbosch na 1997 ma nweta nzere bachelọ na Fine Arts. Ọ bụ ezie na ọ bụ onye na-ese ihe oge niile ugbu a, Aggenbach bụ onye nkuzi site na June 2000 na March 2004 na Cape College na Graphic Processes, Two-Dimensional Design and Drawing. A na-anọchite anya ọrụ ya na Spier Collection, Anglo Gold South Africa, Sasol Art Museum, Sasol Collection, na Hollard Collection.
Usoro afọ 2011 nke mbiputa otu udi nke na-ekwu maka ihe oyiyi na abọm ndị sitere na akụkọ egwu rock
Site na mbipụta ndị a, Aggenbach na-enye nkatọ nke njirimara African er, na-elekwasị anya na ọgbọ nke ndị egwu post-punk kpaliri.
Ihe ngosi 2009 na Gallery AOP sitere n'ike mmụọ nsọ site na njem gaa n'ụlọ Elvis na Memphis, Tennessee, na-enyocha ihe ọ pụtara ịbụ Afrikaans.
Otu ọrụ nke afọ 2008 na-arutu aka na ihe nkiri foto a na-emebi emebi, nke na-eme ka ọdịiche dị n'etiti izi ezi nke foto na ọdịdị na-ezighị ezi ma ọ bụ nke na-eduhie eduhie nke eserese.
